misc
touch is for creating a new file

actual git
git is local
github is the "cloud"
git-DVCS(Distributed Version control software)
repository-directory being tracked using git
start off with git init
to add a file(which already exists) to git repo use:
            git add 'filename' //without quotes
commit is the individual building block of the rep:
            git commit -m "message"
git config --global user.name "name" sets the name
git status tells the status of the rep wrt untracked files and commits
